Diana Letlalo, Vision Works Casual Worker, Refilwe Mabidilala, Practice Manager, Madale Scheepers, Optometrist and Bridgette Ledwaba, Causal Worker celebrate the opening of the new Vision Works practice at Mall of the North. Vision Works enjoys an alliance with Dis-Chem Pharmacies where customers of both businesses are able to enjoy the benefits of special promotions like our R90 cash eye test. Clients can also spend and earn eBucks with us, says Scheepers and encourages the public to enquire how they can benefit at Vision Works. Story and photo: MARKI FRANKEN &gt;&gt;marki.observer@gmail.com &nbsp;